# Crontab for ed-finder maintenance sidecar.
#
# Format: m h dom mon dow command
# Times are UTC.
#
# 03:15 daily — ANALYZE + map MV refresh. Runs after the (assumed
#               post-midnight UTC) Spansh import window so stats are
#               fresh by the time European morning traffic hits.
# 04:00 Sunday — weekly REINDEX + VACUUM ANALYZE.
#
# Output is captured by `crond -f -L /dev/stdout` and tee'd to
# /data/logs/maintenance.log inside the script itself.

15 3 * * *   /usr/local/bin/run_maintenance.sh nightly
 0 4 * * 0   /usr/local/bin/run_maintenance.sh weekly
